---
// Skip-to-main-content accessibility link
// USWDS .usa-skipnav pattern — hidden off-screen, visible on keyboard focus
---

<a
  href="#main-content"
  class="skip-nav pathable-bg-surface pathable-text-primary pathable-font-family-body pathable-padding-y-1 pathable-padding-x-2"
  style="position: absolute; left: 0; top: -100%; z-index: 500; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; outline: none; transition: top 0.1s ease;"
>
  Skip to main content
</a>

<style>
  .skip-nav:focus-visible {
    top: 0;
    outline: 2px solid var(--pathable-color-focus-ring);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>